      <element kind="staticText" x="80" y="360" width="80" height="20">
        <text><![CDATA[For Year-end Reports, you must deliver a copy of this report to your superior officer, along with a copy of the ending bank statement and general ledger/check register. The preferred method is electronically via email. ]]></text>
